metadata.name: This Is Good
metadata.description:
This Is Good is a journey into the blue and the unknown with the gut feeling as a compass. It reminds us of the beautiful moments in life and to listen to our gut feeling rather than fulfilling societal expectations: What feels good has to be good. "This Is Good" encourages us to let ourselves drift and sometimes be irrational.

Cover Design for the song This Is Good from the album "Only in Arts" by electronic/alternative duo whoiswelanski.
https://open.spotify.com/track/64BvTlTVkhxRhzoQgf3khF?si=c4a2d1d2eed4409d

Cover Design by Sandro Rybak
https://www.instagram.com/sandroryry/
https://twitter.com/Sandro_Ryry

The NFT comes with a high quality wav file and a vinyl of the Album "Only in Arts". The vinyl includes a poster with another redeemable NFT.
